WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.458 --> 00:00:03.458
Welcome to the Vivaarium capsule.

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.583
This will be your home for the next 23 years.

3
00:00:09.125 --> 00:00:13.541
You have everything you need for life here.

4
00:00:13.875 --> 00:00:16.250
You wake up in your private chamber,

5
00:00:16.541 --> 00:00:18.916
you wash in the shared shower room,

6
00:00:19.208 --> 00:00:21.416
you dine in the cafeteria.

7
00:00:21.708 --> 00:00:23.208
In case of a health issue,

8
00:00:23.375 --> 00:00:25.166
you can visit the infirmary.

9
00:00:25.541 --> 00:00:28.000
Access to the economic and technical areas

10
00:00:28.291 --> 00:00:30.416
is only granted when the main computer

11
00:00:30.666 --> 00:00:32.625
identifies a problem,

12
00:00:32.875 --> 00:00:34.833
or during an economic day.

13
00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:38.125
Right now, you are in the heart of the capsule -

14
00:00:38.583 --> 00:00:41.083
the community space.

15
00:00:41.458 --> 00:00:44.833
Everything important happens right here.

16
00:00:45.416 --> 00:00:48.791
Safe journey!